com.motorola.mod

Class ModContract

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.motorola.mod.ModContract

  • public final class ModContract
extends Object
    This class defines the content provider for the Moto Mod Manager service.

    The ModManager service exposes a content provider which enables an application to get information about the currently and previously connected Moto Mods. Applications can only query/read the content provider, and not update its records.

    The ModManager content provider will enable an application to retrieve product and vendor information about the connected Moto Mod, the list of protocols supported by the Moto Mod and attachment information.

        public static final Uri CONTENT_URI_MOD

      • CONTENT_URI_MOD_WITH_PROTOCOLS

        public static final Uri CONTENT_URI_MOD_WITH_PROTOCOLS
        This is the URI to get the stats about the Moto Mod including the protocols which the Moto Mod declares support for. This will have multiple entries for each Moto Mod, depending on how many protocols the Moto Mod declares support for.

      • CONTENT_URI_CERT_MOD

        public static final Uri CONTENT_URI_CERT_MOD
        This is the Uri to get the certification status of a Moto Mod. An application can determine whether the attached device is a certified Moto Mod or not.
